OL,3,CHow a cancer diagnosis led Jay to
OL,4,Ccreate Shanika Sunrise
OL,6,FVideo by Granada Reports journalist
OL,7,FAndrew Fletcher
OL,9,FJay Swinnerton was just 19 when they
OL,10,Fwere diagnosed with stage four Hodgkin
OL,11,FLymphoma for the first time.
OL,13,FTheir friends bought them a purple wig
OL,14,Fas they knew that Jay was going to
OL,15,Flose their hair during chemotherapy
OL,16,Fand Shanika Sunrise was born.
