OL,3,CHow a cancer diagnosis led Jay to
OL,4,Ccreate Shanika Sunrise
OL,6,F"I had some very supportive friends
OL,7,Fand they bought me a wig for my
OL,8,Fbirthday. So I started putting this
OL,9,Fwig on and initially started using my
OL,10,FMum's makeup and making videos and it
OL,11,Fall snowballed from there."
OL,13,FLess than a year later Jay was back in
OL,14,Fhospital as it turned out their cancer
OL,15,Fwas refractory, meaning it hadn't
OL,16,Ffully responded to treatment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
