OL,3,CHow a cancer diagnosis led Jay to
OL,4,Ccreate Shanika Sunrise
OL,6,FThey trialled four different drugs and
OL,7,Fjuggled sepsis and lymphoma before
OL,8,Ffinally reaching remission thanks to a
OL,9,Fnew immunotherapy drug that had
OL,10,Frecently been approved on the NHS.
OL,12,FThey also needed a stem cell
OL,13,Ftransplant to narrow the chances of
OL,14,Frelapse. Their brother was a match.
OL,16,FJay turned to drag as a way of dealing
OL,17,Fwith and processing their diagnosis
OL,18,Fand treatment. Performing as Shanika
OL,19,Fhelped them come to terms with what
OL,20,Fwas happening to them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
