OL,3,CHow a cancer diagnosis led Jay to
OL,4,Ccreate Shanika Sunrise
OL,6,FJay says "Shanika Sunrise was born out
OL,7,Fof this time of stress and fear but
OL,8,Fnow she is the reason I get out of bed
OL,9,Fin the morning.
OL,11,FIt's nice now to be able to take to
OL,12,Fthe stage and this be a back story now
OL,13,Fthe reason I do drag is to celebrate
OL,14,Flife and this second chance that I've
OL,15,Fhad."
OL,17,FHanna Simpson is the chief nurse at
OL,18,Fthe Christie looking after teenagers
OL,19,Fand young people. She met Jay when he
OL,20,Fwas 19 and received their diagnosis
OL,21,Fand says they are inspirational:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
