OL,3,CHow a cancer diagnosis led Jay to
OL,4,Ccreate Shanika Sunrise
OL,6,F"Part of my role is to support young
OL,7,Fpeople when they hear those words, you
OL,8,Fhave cancer. 7 young people everyday
OL,9,F16 to 25 hear those words. You want
OL,10,Fhope and you want inspiration, Jay and
OL,11,FShanika combine are a beacon of hope."
OL,13,FShanika Sunrise will be performing on
OL,14,Fthe Alan Turing stage at Manchester
OL,15,FPride in the evening of Saturday 24
OL,16,FAugust.
